ica si alza e il locale con i suoi 119 anni si trasforma in una discoteca alla moda.</p>','Hiltl Langstrasse','Hiltl Langstrasse','Hiltl Langstrasse','Hiltl Langstrasse','Das Hiltl mischt mit Space Brownies, Velo-Drive-Through und versprayten Wänden die Langstrasse auf.','Hiltl on Langstrasse features space brownies, a Bicycle Drive Through, and graffiti-sprayed walls. ','Le Hiltl fait bouger les lignes dans la Langstrasse avec ses brownies, son drive-in et ses graffitis.','Lo Hiltl ravviva la Langstrasse con Space Brownies, drive-through per bici e pareti graffitate.',5128008062,'https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/imagegallery/web_zurich_restaurant_hiltl_langstrasse_buffet.jpg',NULL,NULL,'https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/keyvisual/web_zuerich_hiltl_langstrasse_17699.jpg',NULL,NULL,'2019-11-25 06:55:14 +0100','Reichhaltiges vegetarisch-veganes Hiltl Buffet','First vegetarian restaurant in the world ',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
